{"tid":2046623,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"其實仲有冇細既手機鋪係老實?","createTime":"2020-06-01T13:52:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-05T15:25:24.000Z","uid":160228,"like":3,"dislike":48,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"31f10ff4f4e09daa480ec2606a436890f6c09120","tid":2046623,"uid":160228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T13:52:00.000Z","msg":"話說我部手機真係壞到頂唔順要換 行過信和某手機鋪問左價OK比埋$100訂諗住入手iphone11<br />\n我望住個sales開膠既 但個sales全程冇過叫我check下部機就自己開始幫我過資料 <br />\n加上機身已經有撻唔知咩既污糟野 呢刻我已經覺得好奇怪 正常鋪頭應該都係開完膠拎出黎比你check完 個客話冇問題先開始幫你搞其他野<br />\n不過男朋友有幫我check下機身 我都好放心就繼續坐低等過資料 等左一陣<br />\n之後真係無聊得濟就拎起部機望下 先發現機身左下角位花左 唔算細 係明顯有磨損過個隻 一摸就摸得出<br />\n同個sales講左之後 佢有講番 係新機黎 只係開左機 我先覺得呢間鋪真係唔多老實<br />\n一黎無發現之前 個sales係無講過部機係已經開左機 我當時買既價係$5950 包埋過資料$70<br />\n我冇諗到差唔多6000蚊既價仲會買到開過既機 <br />\n我唔敢講一定係二手 但我覺得多數係 因為個位真係似係人為跌花左 唔似原廠問題 加上sales全程冇叫過我check機 個日打電話問左好多間手機鋪 先達都搵左好多間 都話冇白色 要訂 聽日先有<br />\n冇諗到呢間唯一有現貨既竟然係有問題既貨 <br />\n最後我緊係話唔要 拎番$100訂走左<br />\n<br />\n所以其實係咪真係唔可以貪平去細鋪買手機 差D中伏"},{"pid":"aa58868dcc090b1d7cadbaa898ff6caa6157e40c","tid":2046623,"uid":316700,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T13:54:33.000Z","msg":"驗腦啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a3f3ed42577f365d6677a8c8dc6610037121ade","tid":2046623,"uid":27416,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T13:55:30.000Z","msg":"領域最老實"},{"pid":"0766c92d385d412c22cefbbad4a3e8afb2de16e0","tid":2046623,"uid":109923,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T13:58:23.000Z","msg":"去細鋪買手機貪佢冇信譽？<br />\n<br />\n驗下腦先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb13e5b6d121d8e38d9cb8109f3f7e3bac3108b1","tid":2046623,"uid":134149,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T14:00:29.000Z","msg":"正價賣緊6499 , 去大電器鋪有信用卡優惠加埋回贈都已經平幾百<br />\n<br />\nIphone 過資料已經係兩部機放埋一齊就得<br />\n<br />\n而你竟然覺得6000 係價格ok , 仲要係信和買<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不如慳返筆錢去驗下腦"},{"pid":"404cc6bf97347a1cbbaf9a70d6d6408fbd1e2c01","tid":2046623,"uid":242537,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T14:01:53.000Z","msg":"先達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n先達都搵<br />\n咪買手機住<br />\n去睇腦科先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e96d7298d94ec70c12020559310293f62829eb9f","tid":2046623,"uid":160228,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T14:02:31.000Z","msg":"多謝大家屌醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1063f99be62c35da138764858a94c93fef9f255","tid":2046623,"uid":160228,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T14:03:02.000Z","msg":"我會去番大鋪買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f298efd01aca2e971ef5202a05cf891a117bbee","tid":2046623,"uid":43731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T14:03:29.000Z","msg":"差幾百點解唔去apple?"},{"pid":"3a8116aaaf71e0e20d35254834f136f5591782e3","tid":2046623,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0f298efd01aca2e971ef5202a05cf891a117bbee","tid":2046623,"uid":43731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T14:03:29.000Z","msg":"差幾百點解唔去apple?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T1